name: 7 Sierra Shores Cozy Lakefront Home
description: Enjoy the accommodations of Sierra Shores, a major resort like paradise, private and comfy. Our large very high end 3 bedroom 3 bath townhouse is right on the lake! This property is among the highest end lakefront properties in the entire Lake Tahoe area. Words can't do it justice. Just look at the photos. When you're on the grounds, you will be amazed. With lakefront access and views, this home's grounds and interior are like straight out of a luxury home magazine with the highest quality amenities in the area. You might just have to come up with your own words for it like awespectaculous. From the home, you can walk to numerous shops, restaurants, walk or drive to Heavenly Gondola. There are buoys available to rent to tie up your boat or water toy, just a couple of hundred feet from the property next door.
